title: 820-00165 PP3v42_g3h is 2.5V no light on charger
message:
Hi,

This is pretty clean board no liquid dmg.

PP3v42_G3H is 2.5V and no short on this or any rail. I injected 3.3V to this line and fan spings, charger lights, and works fine.

I replaced I replaced the u7090 and around caps still no change.

Any idea?

title: 820-00165 PP3v42_g3h is 2.5V no light on charger
message:
Check R7095/96 values.
You can play with their values and 3V42 power rail will change accordingly.
